    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
気も遠く世も消え／＼や<lb />
丑三つの森の奥の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">白檀</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">びやくたん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ほのにくゆり<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">木薩地</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こさぢ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>しづき頃ほひ。<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">魑魅</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">すだま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>が気夢にふれて<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">孵</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かへ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>りし<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">我</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">われ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>かの心地。<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">皐月闇</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さつきやみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>霊気ばしる<lb />
夜半の戸に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">額</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ぬか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を垂れて<lb />
あゝ堪へ難き胸の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">狂火</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くるひゞ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>。<lb />
雛よばふ焼野の雉子の<lb />
<lb />
闇睨む眼か　きらに<lb />
燃え飛ぶ野火の遠火の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">青火魂</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あおひだま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>――あなやの刹那。<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">魄霊</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">なほしび</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ゆらに揺ぎつ<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">讃歌</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さんか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">咽喉</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">のみど</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をあふれて<lb />
狂ひ心地、小手招き、<lb />
いと深き闇のをちに<lb />
認め得し小さき<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">焔</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほのほ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">后</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きさい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>。<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">五十年</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いそぢ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のわが歌の世を<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">上下</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かみしも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の永劫に<lb />
うるはしくも<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">霊妙</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いみじ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>く。<lb />
不滅の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">光明</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひかり</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の宮の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">常虹</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">とこにじ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">御座</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">みくら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">上</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">へ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>。<lb />
われ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">生命</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いのち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の王者が<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">斎</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いつ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>かれむほのほの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">后</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きさい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><lb />
猛<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">火</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くわ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">天衣</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">てんね</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">左手</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゆんで</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">着代</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きかへ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をすゝむる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">情</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">じやう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">素振</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">そぶり</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>よ。<lb />
<lb />
この時<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">白隼</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しらはや</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>とびて<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">天</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の世に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">拍手</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はで</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>打つ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">音</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ね</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>もす<lb />
くつがへれ今のこの世<lb />
我こそは<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">理想</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おもひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の宮に<lb />
ひとり笑む王者なるぞ。<lb />
焔そは燃ゆるもの<lb />
身の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">膏</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あぶら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>しぼるものか。<lb />
あゝ好し、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">后</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きさい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">参</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">まゐ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>る。<lb />
焼けても<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">人世</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">じんせ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の外に活くべし。<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
